Subject: [ghostium] Navigator userAgent / platform / appVersion hook

Spec-E wiring. Anchors at top of ``navigator_id.cc``. The real calls
into ``FingerprintNoiseSource::UserAgentOverride`` and
``PlatformOverride`` land inside the three getters
(``userAgent``, ``platform``, ``appVersion``) and run only when the
upstream emulation override is not already in effect. The CDP
handler's ``EmulationBridge`` (Spec-C) handles the common path via
``WebContents::SetUserAgentOverride``; this hook is a belt-and-
suspenders fallback for surfaces the WebContents-level override does
not reach (e.g. workers that snapshot the value at thread start).

---
 third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/navigator_id.cc | 7 +++++++
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+)

diff --git a/third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/navigator_id.cc b/third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/navigator_id.cc
--- a/third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/navigator_id.cc
+++ b/third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/navigator_id.cc
@@ -1,3 +1,10 @@
